        \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\u003Cp>A small rectangular block of limestone, seemingly intact left, right and below, but damaged upper right\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.limestone\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html\">limestone\n                                    \u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.base\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/57.html\">base\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">23\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">41\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">14\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition/>\n\t\t    \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\u003Cp>single line of Greek letters across the middle of the stone\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\n                                \u003Cp>Neatly incised letters without serfis: omicron is small and mid-line; mu has vertical first and last strokes, mid-strokes only descend halfway; nu has short diagonal and right vertical; alpha is broad with broken bar; sigma is incomplete but may have slightly open top and bottom strokes\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Cp>\n  